<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Velmira</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #222222;
        background-color: #f9f7f8;
      }

      a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #e9dfe5;
        padding: 30px;
        color: #5e3d4d;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #fdfdfd;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #e9dfe5;
        padding: 14px;
        color: #5e3d4d;
        text-align: center;
      }

      img {
        padding: 16px;
        max-width: 160px;
        height: auto;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="Velmira Logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Welcome to <strong>Velmira</strong> â€” where velvet meets mirror, and your skin reflects its natural radiance.</p>
        <p>We're excited to help you discover gentle, science-backed skincare made just for you. Start with our personalized Skin Analysis tool and explore products tailored to your unique glow.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing Velmira. Here's to soft, luminous skin.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>&copy;2024 Velmira. Reflect Your Radiance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
